    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140930/extras/1edf26024581352b6e66414204be3767.avif?t=1769787862\" width=636 height=107 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >沉浸在《边缘维度》的演示版中，这为心理恐怖提供了独特的介绍，在这里现实仅仅是一种幻觉。在这个版本中，你将测试你的感官，通过游戏的前三个章节，体验一种徘徊于现实与梦境边缘的氛围。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140930/extras/7f37ce403a534df98f060adbe11e5408.poster.avif?t=1769787862\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140930/extras/7f37ce403a534df98f060adbe11e5408.webm?t=1769787862\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140930/extras/7f37ce403a534df98f060adbe11e5408.mp4?t=1769787862\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >演示版有什么特别之处？</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>有限内容的探索:</strong> 在演示版中，你将只揭示游戏世界的片段，让你熟悉关键机制和氛围，而不会耗尽在完整版中等待你的神秘。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>故事的介绍:</strong> 准备好沉浸于令人不安的叙述和事件，这些事件将在完整版中发展成更复杂的故事。演示版为后续的发现和更大的挑战奠定了基础。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>玩弄感知:</strong> 以更有限的形式体验既视感和迷失感，让你能够掌握游戏机制，而不必面对完整版中等待你的完整旋风。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>心理恐怖:</strong> 发现恐惧如何从更微妙的刺激中产生。在演示版中，你将遇到随着游戏进展而演变的恐惧，但你尚未揭示隐藏在边缘维度深处的所有秘密。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140930/extras/199e49c3f003c17b94ed32727e5e2861.poster.avif?t=1769787862\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140930/extras/199e49c3f003c17b94ed32727e5e2861.webm?t=1769787862\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140930/extras/199e49c3f003c17b94ed32727e5e2861.mp4?t=1769787862\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >你敢揭开《边缘维度》中的秘密吗？</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >将演示版添加到你的愿望清单中，保持关注完整版的发布情况。体验这场非凡冒险的预告，让你渴望探索更多秘密！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140930/extras/75f83232d54a286fc049f1ce5675de7d.poster.avif?t=1769787862\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140930/extras/75f83232d54a286fc049f1ce5675de7d.webm?t=1769787862\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140930/extras/75f83232d54a286fc049f1ce5675de7d.mp4?t=1769787862\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
